EMPTY_QUERY_HINT = "Type a filename, path, or content term. Alt+Up recalls recent queries. Ctrl+D pins the current query."
FILTER_QUERY_HINT = "Refine with ext:, date:, size:, or content: filters. Alt+Up recalls recent queries."
RESULT_LIST_HINT = "Enter opens. Shift+Enter shows properties. Ctrl+Enter reveals. Ctrl+D pins the current query. Tab reaches actions. Alt+C copies path. Alt+N copies name. Alt+1..9 quick-picks. Up/Down wraps. Home/End and PgUp/PgDn jump. Ctrl+A or Ctrl+L returns to filter."
RESULT_QUERY_HINT = "Tab moves through results and actions. Down/Up navigate. Home/End and PgUp/PgDn jump. Enter opens the top hit. Shift+Enter shows properties. Ctrl+D pins the current query. Alt+C copies path. Alt+N copies name. Alt+1..9 quick-picks. Alt+Up recalls recent queries."
